graph LR
    classDef trigger fill:#f9f2f4,stroke:#d0a9b5,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
    classDef process fill:#eef2f5,stroke:#9baebf,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
    classDef decision fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ffb74d,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
    classDef output fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#81c784,stroke-width:2px,color:#333

    Trigger[POST /models/retrain\nmanual or drift-recommended] --> Export[Export Recent Readings\nfrom SQLite to CSV]
    Export --> Candidate[Train Candidate\nIsolation Forest]
    Candidate --> Evaluate[Run evaluate_all.py\non candidate + existing models]
    Evaluate --> Compare{Best model by\nPR-AUC == current production?}
    Compare -->|No| Promote[set_production\nUpdate model_registry.json]
    Promote --> Reload[Reload InferenceService\nlive, zero-downtime]
    Compare -->|Yes| NoOp[No promotion\nkeep current production model]

    class Trigger trigger
    class Export,Candidate,Evaluate process
    class Compare decision
    class Promote,Reload,NoOp output
